"webshop. We process data in accordance with the Law on Personal Data "
"Protection of the Republic of Serbia and, where applicable, the EU General "
"Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)."
msgstr ""
" prodavnicu. Podatke obrađujemo u skladu sa Zakonom o zaštiti podataka o "
"ličnosti Republike Srbije i, gde je primenjivo, GDPR-om."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:7
#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:7
msgid "Last updated: June 2026"
msgstr "Poslednje ažuriranje: jun 2026."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:9
msgid "1. Data controller"
msgstr "1. Rukovalac podacima"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:11
msgid "Controller:"
msgstr "Rukovalac:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:13
msgid "Email:"
msgstr "Email:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:14
msgid "Phone:"
msgstr "Telefon:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:15
msgid "Address:"
msgstr "Adresa:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:18
msgid "2. What data we collect"
msgstr "2. Koje podatke prikupljamo"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:20
msgid "Identity and contact data: name, email, phone, delivery address."
msgstr "Identitet i kontakt: ime, email, telefon, adresa dostave."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:21
msgid ""
"Order data: products ordered, amounts, payment method (cash on delivery), "
"order notes, order number."
msgstr ""
"Podaci o narudžbini: proizvodi, iznosi, način plaćanja (pouzeće), napomene, "
"broj narudžbine."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:22
msgid ""
"Account data (if you register): username, email, password (stored hashed), "
"order history link."
msgstr ""
"Podaci naloga (ako se registrujete): korisničko ime, email, lozinka "
"(heširana), istorija narudžbina."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:23
msgid "Contact form: name, email, optional phone, message content."
msgstr "Kontakt forma: ime, email, opcioni telefon, sadržaj poruke."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:24
msgid ""
"Technical data: IP address, browser type, and logs needed for security and "
"operation."
msgstr ""
"Tehnički podaci: IP adresa, tip pregledača i logovi potrebni za bezbednost i"
" rad sajta."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:27
msgid "3. Purposes and legal bases"
msgstr "3. Svrhe i pravni osnovi"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:32
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "Svrha"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:33
msgid "Legal basis"
msgstr "Pravni osnov"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:38
msgid "Processing and delivering orders"
msgstr "Obrada i isporuka narudžbina"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:39
msgid "Performance of a contract; legal obligation (tax/accounting records)"
msgstr "Izvršenje ugovora; zakonska obaveza (poreski/knjigovodstveni zapisi)"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:42
msgid "Customer accounts and order history"
msgstr "Korisnički nalozi i istorija narudžbina"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:43
msgid "Contract; legitimate interest (customer service)"
msgstr "Ugovor; legitimni interes (korisnička podrška)"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:46
msgid "Contact form and customer support"
msgstr "Kontakt forma i podrška kupcima"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:47
msgid "Legitimate interest; pre-contractual steps at your request"
msgstr "Legitimni interes; predugovorne radnje na vaš zahtev"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:50
msgid "Order and low-stock email notifications"
msgstr "Email obaveštenja o narudžbini i niskim zalihama"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:51
msgid "Contract; legitimate interest (shop operations)"
msgstr "Ugovor; legitimni interes (poslovanje prodavnice)"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:54
msgid "Website security, session, and language preference"
msgstr "Bezbednost sajta, sesija i izbor jezika"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:55
msgid "Legitimate interest; consent where required"
msgstr "Legitimni interes; saglasnost gde je potrebna"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:61
msgid "4. Customer accounts"
msgstr "4. Korisnički nalozi"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:62
msgid ""
"When you register, we store the data needed to identify you and link your "
"orders. You may update your profile through the account area where "
"available. You can request account deletion by contacting us; we may retain "
"certain order records as required by law."
msgstr ""
"Pri registraciji čuvamo podatke potrebne za identifikaciju i povezivanje "
"narudžbina. Profil možete ažurirati u nalogu gde je dostupno. Brisanje "
"naloga zatražite putem kontakta; određene zapise o narudžbinama možemo "
"zadržati u skladu sa zakonom."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:64
msgid "5. Orders"
msgstr "5. Narudžbine"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:65
msgid ""
"Order data is used to fulfil the contract, communicate about delivery, "
"prevent fraud, and maintain business records. We share delivery details with"
" our logistics partners only to the extent necessary to deliver your "
"package."
msgstr ""
"Podatke o narudžbini koristimo za izvršenje ugovora, komunikaciju o dostavi,"
" sprečavanje zloupotrebe i poslovnu evidenciju. Podatke za dostavu delimo sa"
" kurirskim partnerima samo u neophodnoj meri."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:67
msgid "6. Contact forms"
msgstr "6. Kontakt forme"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:68
msgid ""
"Messages you send via the contact form are delivered to our shop email "
"inbox. We use your email to reply. Do not send sensitive health or financial"
" data unless necessary. Spam protection (honeypot) may be used without "
"profiling you."
msgstr ""
"Poruke sa kontakt forme stižu na email prodavnice. Koristimo vaš email za "
"odgovor. Ne šaljite osetljive zdravstvene ili finansijske podatke bez "
"potrebe. Zaštita od spama (honeypot) može se koristiti bez profilisanja."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:70
msgid "7. Cookies and similar technologies"
msgstr "7. Kolačići i slične tehnologije"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:71
msgid ""
"Our storefront uses cookies and similar storage that are necessary for the "
"site to function, including:"
msgstr "Prodavnica koristi kolačiće neophodne za rad sajta, uključujući:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:73
msgid "Session cookie — keeps you logged in and maintains your shopping cart."
msgstr "Sesijski kolačić — održava prijavu i korpu."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:74
msgid "CSRF cookie — protects forms against cross-site request forgery."
msgstr "CSRF kolačić — štiti forme od zloupotrebe."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:75
msgid "Language cookie — remembers your Serbian or English language choice."
msgstr "Jezički kolačić — pamti izbor srpskog ili engleskog jezika."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:77
msgid ""
"We do not use third-party marketing or analytics cookies on the public shop."
" The cookie notice informs you about essential cookies we use. Google Maps "
"is embedded on the contact page and in the footer to show our location; when"
" the map loads, Google may process data (including cookies) under its own "
"privacy policy — see section 10."
msgstr ""
"Ne koristimo marketinške ili analitičke kolačiće trećih strana na javnoj "
"prodavnici. Obaveštenje o kolačićima vas informiše o neophodnim kolačićima "
"koje koristimo. Google Maps je ugrađen na kontakt stranici i u podnožju da "
"prikaže našu lokaciju; kada se mapa učita, Google može obrađivati podatke "
"(uključujući kolačiće) prema svojoj politici privatnosti — pogledajte tačku "
"10."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:79
msgid "8. Analytics"
msgstr "8. Analitika"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:80
msgid ""
"Sales statistics inside our admin panel are generated from order data in our"
" database and are not shared with external analytics providers. The public "
"website does not use Google Analytics or similar visitor tracking at this "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Statistika u admin panelu generiše se iz podataka o narudžbinama u bazi i ne"
" deli se sa spoljnim analitičkim servisima. Javni sajt trenutno ne koristi "
"Google Analytics niti slično praćenje posetilaca."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:82
msgid "9. Email communication"
msgstr "9. Email komunikacija"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:83
msgid ""
"We send transactional emails related to your orders (confirmation to you; "
"operational notices to our team). Email is sent via our configured mail "
"provider (SMTP). You cannot opt out of essential order emails while a "
"contract is active. Marketing emails, if introduced later, will be sent only"
" with your consent and with an unsubscribe option."
msgstr ""
"Šaljemo transakcione emailove vezane za narudžbine (potvrda vama; operativna"
" obaveštenja timu). Email se šalje preko podešenog SMTP provajdera. Ne "
"možete isključiti neophodne emailove dok je ugovor aktivan. Marketinški "
"emailovi, ako budu uvedeni, samo uz saglasnost i opciju odjave."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:85
msgid "10. Google Maps"
msgstr "10. Google Maps"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:86
msgid ""
"Our contact page and footer display an embedded Google Maps map of our store"
" location. The map is loaded from Google’s servers when you open those "
"pages. Google may collect and process personal data (such as IP address and "
"interaction with the map) according to Google’s Privacy Policy and Terms of "
"Service. We use the map to help you find us; we do not control Google’s "
"processing. For questions about our use of the embed, contact us using the "
"details in section 1."
msgstr ""
"Kontakt stranica i podnožje prikazuju ugrađenu Google Maps mapu naše "
"lokacije. Mapa se učitava sa Google servera kada otvorite te stranice. "
"Google može prikupljati i obrađivati lične podatke (npr. IP adresu i "
"interakciju sa mapom) prema Google Politici privatnosti i Uslovima "
"korišćenja. Mapu koristimo da vam pomognemo da nas pronađete; ne "
"kontrolišemo Google obradu. Za pitanja o ugrađenoj mapi kontaktirajte nas "
"putem podataka iz tačke 1."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:87
msgid ""
"This policy is provided for transparency. We recommend that a qualified "
"legal adviser review it for your specific business circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Ova politika je data radi transparentnosti. Preporučujemo da je "
"kvalifikovani pravni savetnik pregleda u skladu sa vašim poslovnim "
"okolnostima."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:89
msgid "11. Retention"
msgstr "11. Čuvanje podataka"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:90
msgid ""
"We keep personal data only as long as needed for the purposes above or as "
"required by law (e.g. accounting archives). Order and invoice data are "
"typically retained for the statutory period applicable in Serbia. Contact "
"form messages are deleted when no longer needed for handling your inquiry."
msgstr ""
"Podatke čuvamo koliko je potrebno za navedene svrhe ili koliko zakon zahteva"
" (npr. knjigovodstvena arhiva). Podaci o narudžbinama se obično čuvaju "
"propisani rok u Srbiji. Poruke sa kontakt forme brišemo kada više nisu "
"potrebne."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:92
msgid "12. Your rights"
msgstr "12. Vaša prava"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:93
msgid ""
"Under applicable law you may request access, correction, deletion, "
"restriction of processing, data portability (where applicable), and object "
"to processing based on legitimate interest. You may withdraw consent at any "
"time without affecting prior lawful processing. You may lodge a complaint "
"with the Commissioner for Information of Public Importance and Personal Data"
" Protection of the Republic of Serbia."
msgstr ""
"U skladu sa zakonom možete zatražiti pristup, ispravku, brisanje, "
"ograničenje obrade, prenosivost (gde se primenjuje) i prigovor na obradu "
"zasnovanu na legitimnom interesu. Saglasnost možete povući u bilo kom "
"trenutku. Žalbu možete podneti Povereniku za informacije od javnog značaja i"
" zaštitu podataka o ličnosti RS."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:94
msgid ""
"To exercise your rights, contact us at the email above. We will respond "
"within the statutory deadline."
msgstr ""
"Za ostvarivanje prava kontaktirajte nas na gornji email. Odgovorićemo u "
"zakonskom roku."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:96
msgid "13. Security"
msgstr "13. Bezbednost"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:97
#, python-format
msgid ""
"We apply appropriate technical and organisational measures (HTTPS in "
"production, access controls, hashed passwords, limited staff access). No "
"method of transmission over the Internet is 100%% secure; please use a "
"strong password for your account."
msgstr ""
"Primenjujemo odgovarajuće tehničke i organizacione mere (HTTPS u produkciji,"
" kontrola pristupa, heširane lozinke). Nijedan prenos preko interneta nije "
"100%% bezbedan; koristite jaku lozinku."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:99
msgid "14. International transfers"
msgstr "14. Međunarodni prenos"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:100
msgid ""
"Data is primarily processed in Serbia/EU hosting. If we use processors "
"outside Serbia/EEA (e.g. email or map providers), we ensure appropriate "
"safeguards such as standard contractual clauses or adequacy decisions where "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Podaci se primarno obrađuju na hostingu u Srbiji/EU. Ako koristimo "
"obrađivače van Srbije/EEA (email, mape), obezbeđujemo odgovarajuće mere "
"zaštite gde je potrebno."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:102
msgid "15. Children"
msgstr "15. Deca"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:103
msgid ""
"Our shop is not directed at children under 15. We do not knowingly collect "
"data from children."
msgstr ""
"Prodavnica nije namenjena deci mlađoj od 15 godina. Svesno ne prikupljamo "
"podatke dece."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:105
msgid "16. Changes"
msgstr "16. Izmene"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_privacy_content.html:106
msgid ""
"We may update this Policy. The current version is always on this page. "
"Significant changes will be communicated where appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Politiku možemo ažurirati. Aktuelna verzija je uvek na ovoj stranici. O "
"značajnim izmenama obavestićemo gde je primereno."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:3
msgid "These Terms of Service govern online sales through the "
msgstr "Ovi Uslovi korišćenja regulišu online prodaju putem "

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:5
msgid ""
"webshop. They are intended for consumers in the Republic of Serbia. This "
"document is for information purposes and does not replace individual legal "
"advice."
msgstr ""
" prodavnice. Namenjeni su potrošačima u Republici Srbiji. Dokument je "
"informativnog karaktera i ne zamenjuje individualni pravni savet."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:9
msgid "1. Seller (operator)"
msgstr "1. Prodavac (operator)"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:11
msgid "The seller operating this webshop is:"
msgstr "Prodavac koji vodi ovu internet prodavnicu je:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:13
msgid "Contact:"
msgstr "Kontakt:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:16
msgid "Registered address:"
msgstr "Adresa sedišta:"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:19
msgid "2. Scope and products"
msgstr "2. Obim i proizvodi"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:20
msgid ""
"We sell mixed/general merchandise through this website. Product "
"descriptions, photos, and prices shown on product pages form part of the "
"offer. We reserve the right to correct obvious errors and to update the "
"assortment."
msgstr ""
"Prodajemo mešovitu/raznovrsnu robu putem ovog sajta. Opisi, fotografije i "
"cene na stranicama proizvoda čine deo ponude. Zadržavamo pravo ispravke "
"očiglednih grešaka i ažuriranja asortimana."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:22
msgid "3. Account and guest checkout"
msgstr "3. Nalog i kupovina bez naloga"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:23
msgid ""
"You may place orders as a guest or after creating a customer account. You "
"are responsible for keeping your login credentials confidential and for "
"activity under your account. Account data is processed according to our "
"Privacy Policy."
msgstr ""
"Možete poručiti kao gost ili nakon registracije. Odgovorni ste za čuvanje "
"pristupnih podataka i aktivnosti na nalogu. Podaci naloga se obrađuju prema "
"Politici privatnosti."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:25
msgid "4. Ordering process"
msgstr "4. Proces poručivanja"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:26
msgid ""
"By submitting an order you make a binding purchase offer. We confirm receipt"
" by email. A sales contract is concluded when we accept the order "
"(confirmation or dispatch). Before placing an order you must accept these "
"Terms and our Privacy Policy."
msgstr ""
"Slanjem narudžbine dajete obavezujuću ponudu za kupovinu. Potvrdu prijema "
"šaljemo emailom. Ugovor o prodaji nastaje kada prihvatimo narudžbinu. Pre "
"poručivanja morate prihvatiti ove Uslove i Politiku privatnosti."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:28
msgid "You must provide accurate contact and delivery details."
msgstr "Morate uneti tačne kontakt i podatke za dostavu."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:29
msgid "Prices are shown in Serbian dinars (RSD) unless stated otherwise."
msgstr "Cene su u dinarima (RSD) osim ako nije drugačije naznačeno."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:30
msgid "Delivery cost is calculated at checkout based on the selected city."
msgstr "Cena dostave se računa pri plaćanju prema izabranom gradu."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:33
msgid "5. Prices and payment"
msgstr "5. Cene i plaćanje"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:34
msgid ""
"All prices include applicable VAT where required by law. Payment is made on "
"delivery (cash on delivery) unless we explicitly offer another method. You "
"pay the courier upon receipt of the goods in cash or by card if available."
msgstr ""
"Sve cene uključuju PDV gde zakon zahteva. Plaćanje je pouzećem osim ako "
"eksplicitno ponudimo drugi način. Kuriru plaćate pri preuzimanju gotovinom "
"ili karticom ako je dostupno."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:36
msgid "6. Delivery"
msgstr "6. Dostava"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:37
msgid ""
"We deliver within the Republic of Serbia to the address you provide. "
"Estimated delivery times are indicative and may depend on the carrier and "
"your location. Risk of accidental loss or damage passes to you when you take"
" physical possession of the goods."
msgstr ""
"Dostavljamo na teritoriji Republike Srbije na adresu koju navedete. Rokovi "
"su orientacioni i zavise od kurira i lokacije. Rizik slučajnog gubitka "
"prelazi na vas pri preuzimanju robe."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:39
msgid "7. Right of withdrawal (consumers)"
msgstr "7. Pravo na odustanak (potrošači)"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:40
msgid ""
"If you are a consumer under Serbian consumer protection law, you may "
"withdraw from a distance contract within 14 days of receiving the goods, "
"without giving a reason, subject to legal exceptions (e.g. sealed goods that"
" cannot be returned for hygiene reasons, custom-made items, perishable "
"goods). To exercise withdrawal, notify us clearly at our contact email "
"before the deadline expires."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste potrošač po zakonu o zaštiti potrošača, možete odustati od ugovora "
"na daljinu u roku od 14 dana od prijema robe, bez navođenja razloga, osim "
"izuzetaka propisanim zakonom (npr. zapečaćena roba, proizvodi po meri, "
"kvarljiva roba). Obaveštenje pošaljite na kontakt email pre isteka roka."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:41
msgid ""
"You must return the goods without undue delay and in any event within 14 "
"days of sending your withdrawal notice. You bear direct return costs unless "
"we agree otherwise or the law requires us to bear them. We will refund "
"payments using the same means of payment, after we receive the goods or "
"proof of return, in accordance with applicable law."
msgstr ""
"Robu vratite bez odlaganja, najkasnije u roku od 14 dana od obaveštenja o "
"odustanku. Troškove povratne dostave snosite vi, osim ako drugačije ne "
"ugovorimo ili zakon ne nalaže drugačije. Uplatu vraćamo istim sredstvom "
"plaćanja nakon prijema robe ili dokaza o povratu, u skladu sa zakonom."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:43
msgid "8. Complaints and conformity of goods"
msgstr "8. Reklamacije i usaglašenost robe"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:44
msgid ""
"If goods are non-conforming or defective, you may submit a complaint within "
"the statutory period. Contact us with your order number and a description of"
" the issue. We will respond in line with the Law on Consumer Protection and "
"related regulations."
msgstr ""
"Ako roba nije usaglašena ili je neispravna, možete podneti reklamaciju u "
"zakonskom roku. Kontaktirajte nas sa brojem narudžbine i opisom problema. "
"Postupićemo u skladu sa Zakonom o zaštiti potrošača i propisima."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:46
msgid "9. Limitation of liability"
msgstr "9. Ograničenje odgovornosti"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:47
msgid ""
"We are liable for damage caused intentionally or through gross negligence. "
"For consumers, mandatory statutory rights are not limited. For business "
"buyers, liability is limited to the maximum extent permitted by law. We are "
"not responsible for indirect loss or delays caused by force majeure or "
"third-party carriers beyond our reasonable control."
msgstr ""
"Odgovorni smo za štetu prouzrokovanu namerno ili krajnjom nepažnjom. Za "
"potrošače se ne ograničavaju obavezna zakonska prava. Za pravna lica "
"odgovornost je ograničena u meri dozvoljenoj zakonom. Nismo odgovorni za "
"neizravnu štetu ili kašnjenja usled više sile ili kurira van naše razumne "
"kontrole."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:49
msgid "10. Intellectual property"
msgstr "10. Intelektualna svojina"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:50
msgid ""
"Website content (text, images, logos, software) is protected by copyright "
"and other rights. You may not copy or use it without our prior written "
"consent except for personal browsing and ordering."
msgstr ""
"Sadržaj sajta (tekst, slike, logotipi, softver) je zaštićen autorskim i "
"drugim pravima. Ne smete ga kopirati bez naše pisane saglasnosti, osim za "
"lično pregledanje i poručivanje."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:52
msgid "11. Personal data"
msgstr "11. Lični podaci"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:54
msgid "Processing of personal data is described in our"
msgstr "Obrada ličnih podataka opisana je u našoj"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:58
msgid "12. Dispute resolution"
msgstr "12. Rešavanje sporova"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:59
msgid ""
"We aim to resolve complaints amicably. Consumers may also contact the "
"competent market inspection authority or use out-of-court dispute resolution"
" bodies where available under Serbian law. The courts of the Republic of "
"Serbia have jurisdiction unless mandatory consumer rules provide otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Težimo da reklamacije rešimo mirno. Potrošači mogu kontaktirati nadležnu "
"inspekciju tržišta ili koristiti vansudsko rešavanje sporova gde je "
"dostupno. Za sudove je nadležna Republika Srbija, osim ako obavezna pravila "
"o potrošačima ne predviđaju drugačije."

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:61
msgid "13. Changes"
msgstr "13. Izmene"

#: .\templates\includes\legal\_terms_content.html:62
msgid ""
"We may update these Terms. The version published on this page applies to "
"orders placed after publication. Material changes will be highlighted on the"
" website where appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Uslove možemo ažurirati. Verzija objavljena na ovoj stranici važi za "
"narudžbine posle objavljivanja. Bitne izmene ćemo istaknuti na sajtu gde je "
"primereno."

